    "However, our framework shifts the perspective to the aggregate level, where we model and characterize a conceptually similar form of functional parallelism at the distributional level.",
    "Estimating the unknown ESE mappings f t is still challenging in practice.",
    "With only a single realization of the outcome panel, the information available for learning these mappings is limited.",
